label.value: cell body rind of larval ventrolateral antennal lobe

value.value: Region of the cell body rind overlying the ventrolateral part of the larval antennal lobe. Some antennal lobe local neurons have their cell bodies here (Thum et al., 2011; Liou et al., 2018).

label.value: cell body rind of larval dorsolateral antennal lobe

value.value: Region of the cell body rind overlying the dorsolateral part of the larval antennal lobe. Some antennal lobe local neurons have their cell bodies here (Thum et al., 2011; Liou et al., 2018).

label.value: CNMamide neuron

value.value: Any neuron (FBbt:00005106) that is capable of some peptide hormone secretion (GO:0030072) and expresses CNMa (FBgn0035282).

label.value: leg taste bristle mechanosensory neuron

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that innervates a leg taste bristle.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of femoral chordotonal organ

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that innervates a scolopidium of a femoral chordotonal organ. Each scolopidium is innervated by two such neurons (Shanbhag et al., 1992; Kuan et al., 2020). There are around 135 per leg and they project through the leg nerve to the ventral nerve cord, with a small minority (3-4) continuing to the brain (Mamiya et al., 2018; Phelps et al., 2021). They are cholinergic proprioceptive sensory neurons (Mamiya et al., 2018; Agrawal et al., 2020).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of prothoracic femoral chordotonal organ

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that innervates a scolopidium of a femoral chordotonal organ in the prothoracic leg. There are 152 such neurons in a prothoracic leg (Kuan et al., 2020).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of metathoracic femoral chordotonal organ

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that innervates a scolopidium of a femoral chordotonal organ in the metathoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of mesothoracic femoral chordotonal organ

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that innervates a scolopidium of a femoral chordotonal organ in the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: campaniform sensillum of leg

value.value: Campaniform sensillum that is found on a leg.

label.value: campaniform sensillum of trochanter

value.value: Campaniform sensillum located in the trochanter.

label.value: sensory neuron of campaniform sensillum

value.value: Sensory neuron of a campaniform sensillum.

definition.value: Some of these seem to be octopaminergic based on Tdc2-GAL4 expression (Pauls et al., 2018 - FBrf0240407).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of leg campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the leg. Its axon terminals are found in the middle of the leg neuropil, relatively dorsal compared to other sensory neurons (Tsubouchi et al., 2017).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of trochanter campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the trochanter.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of femoral campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the femur.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of coxal hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the coxa.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of prothoracic coxal hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the coxa of the prothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of mesothoracic coxal hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the coxa of the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of metathoracic coxal hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the coxa of the metathoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of trochanter hair plate

value.value: A mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the trochanter. Its axonal projection enters the VNC through the prothoracic leg nerve (Kuan et al., 2020).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of prothoracic trochanter hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the trochanter of the prothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of mesothoracic trochanter hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the trochanter of the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of metathoracic trochanter hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the trochanter of the metathoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of metathoracic hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the metathoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of mesothoracic hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of prothoracic hair plate

value.value: Any mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a hair plate of the prothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of prothoracic femoral campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the femur of the prothoracic leg. Its axonal projection enters the VNC through the prothoracic leg nerve (Kuan et al., 2020).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of mesothoracic femoral campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the femur of the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of metathoracic femoral campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the femur of the metathoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of prothoracic trochanter campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the trochanter of the prothoracic leg. Its axonal projection enters the VNC through the prothoracic leg nerve (Kuan et al., 2020).

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of mesothoracic trochanter campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the trochanter of the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: mechanosensory neuron of metathoracic trochanter campaniform sensillum

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron with a dendrite in a campaniform sensillum of the trochanter of the metathoracic leg.

label.value: prothoracic bristle

value.value: Any chaeta found in the prothoracic segment of the adult.

label.value: leg mechanosensory bristle

value.value: Any chaeta that is a part of the leg and is involved in the detection of mechanical stimuli.

label.value: prothoracic leg mechanosensory bristle

value.value: Any chaeta that is a part of the prothoracic leg and is involved in the detection of mechanical stimuli.

label.value: metathoracic leg mechanosensory bristle

value.value: Any chaeta that is a part of the metathoracic leg and is involved in the detection of mechanical stimuli.

label.value: mesothoracic leg mechanosensory bristle

value.value: Any chaeta that is a part of the mesothoracic leg and is involved in the detection of mechanical stimuli.

label.value: leg mechanosensory bristle mechanosensory neuron

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a mechanosensory bristle of the leg.

label.value: prothoracic leg bristle mechanosensory neuron

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a mechanosensory bristle of the prothoracic leg.

label.value: metathoracic leg bristle mechanosensory neuron

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a mechanosensory bristle of the metathoracic leg.

label.value: mesothoracic leg bristle mechanosensory neuron

value.value: Mechanosensory neuron that has a dendrite in a mechanosensory bristle of the mesothoracic leg.

label.value: adult intersegmental mechanosensory system neuron

value.value: Ascending neuron of the adult with its dendrites in multiple thoracic neuromeres of the ventral nerve cord. It is downstream of ipsilateral mechanosensory leg bristle neurons and femoral chordotonal organ neurons.

label.value: adult midline local mechanosensory system neuron

value.value: Neuron of the adult with its dendrites in the ventral parts of one thoracic neuromere in one hemisphere of the ventral nerve cord. It is downstream of ipsilateral mechanosensory leg bristle neurons.

label.value: adult midline bilateral mechanosensory system neuron

value.value: Neuron of the adult that arborizes mainly in one hemisphere of the ventral nerve cord, but also sends out a projection to the other. It is downstream of ipsilateral and contralateral mechanosensory leg bristle neurons.

label.value: adult intrinsic nodulus neuron

value.value: Large field neuron that innervates only the noduli. One of these neurons, arborizing in both hemispheres, was identified by Hanesh et al. (1989).

label.value: adult intrinsic lateral accessory lobe neuron

value.value: Large field neuron that innervates only the lateral accessory lobe. One of these neurons, arborizing in both hemispheres, was identified by Hanesch et al. (1989).

label.value: adult antennal lobe projection neuron VP2 adPN

value.value: Adult uniglomerular antennal lobe projection neuron that develops from the ALad1 neuroblast and has dendrites that mainly innervate antennal lobe glomerulus VP2 (Stocker et al., 1990; Marin et al., 2020). It projects via the medial antennal lobe tract to arborize in the mushroom body calyx, lateral accessory calyx and the lateral horn (Stocker et al., 1990; Marin et al., 2020). There is one of these per hemisphere and it is cholinergic (Marin et al., 2020).

label.value: adult antennal lobe projection neuron DP1

value.value: Adult uniglomerular antennal lobe projection neuron with dendrites that mainly innervate antennal lobe glomerulus DP1.

label.value: eclosion hormone neuron

value.value: Any neuron (FBbt:00005106) that is capable of some peptide hormone secretion (GO:0030072) and expresses Eh (FBgn0000564).

label.value: adult antennal lobe projection neuron DA1

value.value: Adult uniglomerular antennal lobe projection neuron whose dendrites mainly innervate antennal lobe glomerulus DA1.
